    <main>
        <div class="container1">
            <h1 class="title " style="padding:35px 0px 0px 100px;">Plasma Donation</h1>
            <p class="para " style=" padding:20px 100px 70px 100px;">
                Our clinic is dedicated to ensuring the well-being of all individuals within our community. 
                We recognize the vital importance of plasma donation in saving lives and sustaining health. 
                Our team is committed to facilitating and promoting plasma donation initiatives, fostering a
                culture of compassion and generosity among our patients and staff. Whether through organizing 
                plasma drives, providing information on donation procedures, or supporting donors throughout 
                the process, we strive to contribute to the noble cause of enhancing the availability of 
                life-saving plasma for those in need. Your participation in this essential act of giving is 
                deeply appreciated and makes a significant impact on the lives of others.
            </p>
        </div>

